name: George Powell
description:
Hello am george powell by name, am male 55 single and widower with 2 kids and wife passed away some years ago and from conway,arkansas and am honest, good, caring, friendly and am trustworthy and also cheerful to people around the world and in different part of the earth.
for me i love to make good friends,play indoors and outdoors games and love to sing and dance to good and cool music and love to make use of my computer and spend time with my friends and love to travel and visit good cities and states and love to watch tv during leisure time like movies,documentaries, and entertainment and love to write poems.
